high_descs: Pick up the large pan from the stove.
Bring the pan to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink and fill it with water.
Bring the pan with water back to the white table.
Put the pan on the table.
Turn to the right and move towards the wall then turn right and move to the front of the stove in the corner of the room.
Pick up the dirty pan from the front right burner of the stove closest to the table.
Turn right and move past the table to the sink next to the microwave.
Place the dirty pan in the sink and clean it. Fill the pan with water then turn off the faucet.
Turn around and move towards the end of the room with the refrigerator and oven. Turn right and face the center of the table.
Place the pan of water in the center of the table next to the oven.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean pan of water on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove to your left.
Take the pan nearest to you from the stove.
Turn to your right and go to the sink in front of you.
Fill the pan in the sink with water.
Turn around and go to the table ahead of you and to the right.
Place the pan on the center of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a water-filled pan on a table.
